{"tid":1655934,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"工程界人士一啲advice","createTime":"2019-10-15T10:24:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-15T12:01:39.000Z","uid":124690,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"476e65b69a13d9fcb155145a16c1bf0c32926422","tid":1655934,"uid":124690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T10:24:09.000Z","msg":"你地經常搭嘅升降機<br />\n如果有水整濕井道（𨋢糟）入面嘅野<br />\n客方就要俾返相應嘅人工同埋料錢<br />\n俾𨋢公司整返<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n咩時候會發生？<br />\n通常都會經升降機大堂滲水而整濕內部部件<br />\n雖然看似行得走得<br />\n但極可能背後升降機公司以經報緊價叫客方俾錢<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n你地平時見到嘅升降機掣<br />\n計曬人工我諗都要一千蚊一粒<br />\n如果你見到佢冇鏍絲收實<br />\n恭喜曬<br />\n你可以就咁挑成塊板出嚟<br />\n所以千奇唔好試圖挑佢出嚟<br />\n如果啲線斷左其實駁返就用到<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n最後 講左咁多 大家千奇唔好做<br />\n我只係提醒大家點樣維持一個良好使用升降機方法"},{"pid":"08e5408f5d0e0d07dabc987d07608aa984de5d36","tid":1655934,"uid":124690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T10:24:41.000Z","msg":"推下"},{"pid":"c8b25e15e3e4722a31403bed1849ecfd6c9040ef","tid":1655934,"uid":124690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T10:24:58.000Z","msg":"再推"},{"pid":"f877a5564e6f9f62749c603b7b04de1481abcd97","tid":1655934,"uid":47042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T10:25:33.000Z","msg":"大家唔好亂黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18e4990f4aa5454bd3883fd17467df45667f4850","tid":1655934,"uid":124690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T10:26:54.000Z","msg":"教學就教曬<br />\n大家以後應該都識得點搭lift"},{"pid":"2ed04c90f168e0e6890cd010b33d80412afc2fe4","tid":1655934,"uid":6882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T10:27:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1ace9d70d5bd095117023c77a660ef6042aa691f","tid":1655934,"uid":124690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T10:27:56.0